WEBVTT

00:02:55.830 --> 00:03:04.305
because if I cry I'd give in to fear.

00:03:04.305 --> 00:03:12.110
I must be strong, have to hold on.

00:03:12.110 --> 00:03:16.029
Gotta get through

00:03:16.029 --> 00:03:20.378
another year.

00:03:20.378 --> 00:03:25.881
I am a prisoner
for the wrong I've done.

00:03:25.881 --> 00:03:29.573
I'm doing time here.
This is not my home.

00:03:29.573 --> 00:03:34.658
Dream of freedom, hope for mercy.